original_title: Shape Pink Power Flat Abs 5 Ways - FAT FREE CARDIO AB BLAST
overview: In this section, Smith alternates brief cardio bursts with "recovery" moves. Several of the moves involve jumping in and out of a plank position, including a squat thrust and a plank ski jump. Recovery moves were move basic, such as knee raises and v-sits.
title: Shape Pink Power Flat Abs 5 Ways - FAT FREE CARDIO AB BLAST
